係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港四罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈麻包袋都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#重組警隊 改革監警制度<br />\n#永遠不光顧荃灣北角元朗商戶<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動"},{"pid":"b6769de8ca253e02882941de4af3fec018aeb775","tid":1490553,"uid":116478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:03:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}